q 0.4 G 1 w 36 600 m 396 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 575 Td (Week 1: Download a voice recording app and record 3 memories \(any length, any topic\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 554 Td (Week 2: Scan 10-20 of your most important old photographs using your phone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 533 Td (Week 3: Use ChatGPT to organize your memories into a rough outline of your story.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 512 Td (Week 4: Write or record one complete chapter about your childhood or family of origin.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 491 Td (Month 2: Continue recording one chapter per week. Scan more photos and documents.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 470 Td (Month 3: Begin AI photo restoration on your most damaged and precious images.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 449 Td (Month 4: Create a family cookbook by recording recipes and their stories.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 428 Td (Month 5: Research your genealogy using AI tools to add ancestral context.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 407 Td (Month 6: Compile everything into a organized digital archive with family access.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 386 Td (Ongoing: Continue adding stories, photos, and wisdom as inspiration strikes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 365 Td (Remember: Imperfect preservation is infinitely better than perfect silence.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 344 Td (Start with whatever you can, today. Your story is already being lost to time.) Tj ET

